## build on rock 5b host
```sh
$ sudo apt-get install libcairo2-dev libcairo2 libprocps-dev libprocps8 libkmod-dev libkmod2 -y

$ meson build && ninja -C build

$ sudo cp /usr/lib/aarch64-linux-gnu/* /data/nfs_rootfs/usr/lib/aarch64-linux-gnu/
```

## Testing
```
$ ./kms_writeback IGT_DEVICE="sys:/sys/devices/platform/vkms"
```

## Usage

[Test With IGT](https://dri.freedesktop.org/docs/drm/gpu/vkms.html)
[igt-gpu-tools](https://drm.pages.freedesktop.org/igt-gpu-tools/)